{"tid":2495514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓最正姊妹合體！潔西卡「泳裝照」被流出　粉絲嗨翻了","createTime":"2021-04-19T08:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:17:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7df7c75b51e4ab06a1349f6d4192cc67d8df2b79","tid":2495514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女星潔西卡（鄭秀妍）與妹妹Krystal（鄭秀晶），是南韓演藝圈眾所皆知的高顏值姊妹。18日正是潔西卡的32歲生日，結果卻被妹妹出賣一張，兩人罕見合體的泳裝照，小露性感的氛圍讓粉絲又驚又喜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/19/3117053-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F19%2F3117053-PH.jpg&h=43b1acfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姊妹倆罕見泳裝合體，扮鬼臉小露性感，送給粉絲驚喜。（圖／翻攝自Krystal IG）<br />\n<br />\nKrystal昨日在IG上曬出和姊姊潔西卡的合照，只見姊妹倆分別穿上泳裝小露性感，特別的是，鮮少合體的姊妹倆，一貼出照片就是兩人的泳裝照，讓粉絲相當驚訝，另一張則是兩人一起俏皮嘟嘴扮鬼臉的照片，而且Krystal還被姊姊逗笑，對向來以高冷形象示人的Krystal來說非常特別。<br />\n<br />\n雖然不常在鏡頭前面合體，但兩人常常會出現在彼此的IG動態中，一舉一動就可以看出兩人的深厚感情，此外，Krystal更在貼文中對姊姊喊話「祝我獨一無二的姊姊生日快樂！妳知道我愛妳！」照片曝光後，立刻吸引粉絲朝聖，「好美啊！」「真姊妹花」、「還以為是雙胞胎呢」。<br />\n<br />\n從韓國女團「少女時代」出身的潔西卡，不僅發行過專輯和單曲，在戲劇節目、主持上表現亮眼，而妹妹Krystal也是從女團f(x)出道，和姊姊一樣多方位發展，近年來更專注在戲劇方面，其演出作品包括《繼承者們》、《Player》、《Search》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/06/18/562226-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F06%2F18%2F562226-PH.jpg&h=3b39724c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潔西卡前些年多次來台表演，台灣粉絲非常多。（圖／資料照）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/19/3117059-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F19%2F3117059-PH.jpg&h=a11ef47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲（左）Krystal多以高冷的形象出現，偶爾會在姐姐面前露出微笑。（圖／翻攝自Krystal IG）"},{"pid":"d2ed98aee04ec76c6e00f13dd873539f18a72d89","tid":2495514,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"正..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d257bd6ec0050fb1f4a79ae23e122cac66d6520","tid":2495514,"uid":313222,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9716bfc91c561f6f08287f55bbac5f4dd2d045","tid":2495514,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"幾時返黎唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4cfba7da124c30d08ed7afeca7abf8bdc86307b","tid":2495514,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"姊妹井<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b685a6e84c00ea642d3b1cef8419dac1a2cef76","tid":2495514,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"Jessica<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a45c140fe66358548da833c4c6ad1c3026a4f1","tid":2495514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd9716bfc91c561f6f08287f55bbac5f4dd2d045","tid":2495514,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"幾時返黎唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"再見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271318ce9a0d32fe006cc8afab1a5fc82d67caf2","tid":2495514,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a45c140fe66358548da833c4c6ad1c3026a4f1","tid":2495514,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pi